 <h1>
Welcome to CK Casting - a new and exciting agency for babies &amp; toddlers to young
adults. We specialise in film, TV, commercial and theatrical casting. We know that
you will find working with our children a successful and pleasureable experience.
</h1>
<p><b>CK Casting offers so much more...</b></p>
<ul>
    <li>A specialised agency, solely representing children, young adults, siblings and twins.</li>
    <li>A site designed exclusively for casting professionals.</li>
    <li>Highly-experienced and trained child actors, singers and dancers.</li>
    <li>Children attend regular classes to maintain a high standard of performance.</li>
    <li>All children are based within easy access to Central London.</li>
    <li>We are happy to arrange performance licences as required, quickly and free of charge.</li>
    <li>We are constantly updating our files with new children joining throughout the year.</li>
</ul>



